      "## Choosing the Right Venue",
      "For mega-exhibitions (1,000+ exhibitors, 50,000+ visitors), the options in Riyadh are limited to RICEC and a small number of purpose-adapted venues. Ensure your chosen venue has the infrastructure to support [corporate event](/services/corporate-events) technologies: high-density Wi-Fi throughout the show floor, sufficient power distribution for complex stands, loading dock capacity that matches your move-in schedule, and adequate floor load ratings for heavy industrial exhibits. Demand for large-scale exhibition space is at an all-time high — book early.",
