      "[Jeddah Season](/locations/jeddah) transforms the city into one of the most active entertainment markets in the region. For corporations planning client events, team activations, or brand experiences during the season, it creates both an opportunity — heightened appetite for entertainment among your target audience — and a challenge: standing out when the city is full of competing high-quality events.",
      "Aligning [corporate events](/services/corporate-events) with Jeddah Season gives brands a built-in cultural context. The key is choosing activations that fit your brand and your audience rather than simply importing what worked for someone else.",
      "## 1. Interactive Digital Art Installations",
